body_html: Tensorflow 1.6 and above supports CPUs without avx. It is the official release binary (the one you download from pip) that does not support CPUs without avx. To use Tensorflow on old CPUs you'll need to build a binary on your own.

body: Tensorflow 1.6 and above __supports__ CPUs without avx. It is the official release binary (the one you download from pip) that does not support CPUs without avx. To use Tensorflow on old CPUs you'll need to build a binary on your own.
